org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge.json

Class JCgetScenes.BCproductState

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge.json.JCgetScenes.BCproductState
  • Enclosing class:
    JCgetScenes

    @NonNullByDefault
private static class JCgetScenes.BCproductState
extends java.lang.Object
    Bridge Communication Structure containing the state of a product.

    Therefore it includes the typeId and name identifying the product, as well as actuator and status.

    Used within structure JCgetScenes.BCscene to describe the final states of the products belonging to this scene. 

     "typeId": 2,
 "name": "Rolladen Schlafzimmer",
 "actuator": 0,
 "status": 0
